 />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=bb363f5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6699f1f141f14fb9ce7ee5c6a086f69aeedb2de","tid":1518123,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"大台: 香港遊樂場協會"},{"pid":"185d87e501317229f44992c038f56eb76b5cd834","tid":1518123,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdcb233367016a6a016c75e48d8dec266a28ebc1","tid":1518123,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"想知大家幾時先玩夠 唔好再當香港係遊樂場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無視佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"佢地有d覺得你地根本只係單方面俾黑警打<br />\n破壞只流於小兒科<br />\n同真正既暴亂規模差好遠<br />\n文革、67暴動等等<br />\n<br />\n所以成日會話你地係&rdquo;玩&rdquo;"},{"pid":"03799d0c13cd47a6395500162c3078d1bd31d6c0","tid":1518123,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco